---
source: cli/tests/help.rs
expression: "help(&[\"qgroup\", \"create\"])"
---
Create a subvolume quota group

Usage: create <QGROUPID> <PATH>

Arguments:
  <QGROUPID>
          Qgroup id in the form LEVEL/ID

  <PATH>
          Path to a mounted btrfs filesystem

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
